                            <comment id="13011324" author="gagravarr" created="Fri, 25 Mar 2011 18:12:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The patch NPOIFS-3.8beta2.diff depends on the latest POI snapshot, so can&apos;t be applied until 3.8 beta 2 is out. However, it allows all unit tests to pass when using NPOIFS (and also includes TNEF which depends on 3.8 beta 2), so can be applied as soon as the new POI release is out&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
